scsi_block_when_processing_errors \- Prevent cmds from being queued\&.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'int\ scsi_block_when_processing_errors('u
.BI "int scsi_block_when_processing_errors(struct\ scsi_device\ *\ " "sdev" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIsdev\fR
